{
  "stem": "17626.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 143.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we didn't observe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There wasn't even 10 people to have a minion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now I work for a Jewish synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, and for a Holocaust Jewish synagogue to begin with, I can tell you all sorts about the holidays.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In those days, I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not until we came to Germany that that became clearer, what Judaism, holidays, what it was all about.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in 1945, when the war ended, again, these cattle cars were provided.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Polish citizens who did not take the Russian passports out, were allowed to leave Russia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The whole idea was that they kept offering to the Polish people to become Russian citizens.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some of them did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some of them intermarried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and they had to stay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They stayed in, in Russia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But all those who did not take the-- out the Russian citizenship, via passports were permitted to leave Russia and go back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now this [NON-ENGLISH] that we were on headed for Poland, was destined for the Polish corridor, for the place that previously was Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they wanted to settle with Polish citizens that part of previous Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I can't remember how long, but it was certainly several weeks where we slept on straw and ate whatever we could, and the cattle cars were also provided with potbellied stoves.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, it was fairly cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we got as-- into Poland, and my mother and her friend Tosia, and Rachel, and I; the four of us, my mother jumped off the train when it hit [?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Walpshich. ?] That was already the last city before that Polish corridor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We got off, and they took us off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we-- the train continued.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we stayed in [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Walpshich. ?] And that was a revelation.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
